An allowance of 4.5 W is provided for each Ethernet Point-to-Point 1 Gbit/s interface for MCMTS Core and Edge-QAM. An allowance of 8 W is provided for each M-CMTS Ethernet Point-to-Point 10 Gbit/s interface for M-CMTS core and Edge-QAM.

